00:45:29.390 --> 00:45:30.460
RICHARD THALER: Right.

00:45:30.460 --> 00:45:39.330
So I think that
models can hide a lot.

00:45:39.330 --> 00:45:48.070
And I think the idea that
you can't learn anything

00:45:48.070 --> 00:45:51.590
without a model is preposterous.

00:45:51.590 --> 00:45:56.590
So there's no model
in our football paper.

00:45:56.590 --> 00:45:58.460
But look at those graphs.

00:45:58.460 --> 00:46:01.890
They tell a pretty
