equal to intrinsic value.

00:46:11.680 --> 00:46:13.520
And in order to get
the paper published,

00:46:13.520 --> 00:46:16.049
we put in some Greek symbols.

00:46:16.049 --> 00:46:18.090
AUDIENCE: But what I wonder
