00:46:23.940 --> 00:46:26.400
both popular and contradictory?

00:46:26.400 --> 00:46:29.290
RICHARD THALER:
You use whichever

00:46:29.290 --> 00:46:32.495
one comes in handy at the time.

00:46:35.330 --> 00:46:39.800
That may sound
