00:46:52.180 --> 00:46:54.530
hiding under there somewhere,
whether people are getting

00:46:54.530 --> 00:46:55.470
it right or wrong.

00:46:55.470 --> 00:46:57.220
And I wonder what
you think of the idea

00:46:57.220 --> 00:47:01.750
that there may not be the,
that the right price is just

00:47:01.750 --> 00:47:03.190
defined by whatever
